      "question": "A spiral is made up of successive semicircles, with centers alternately at A and B, starting with center at A of radii $0.5 cm, 1.0 cm, 1.5 cm, 2.0 cm, ...$. What is the total length of such a spiral made up of thirteen consecutive semicircles? (Take $\\pi = \\frac{22}{7}$)",
